# Project Context

This is a monorepo with 0 packages indexed by boocontext.
Read `..boocontext/BOOCONTEXT.md` for the full package index — it lists every package that has a context file.

Before exploring a package directory, check if `<package>/..boocontext/BOOCONTEXT.md` exists — faster than grep/find.
Use `<package>/..boocontext/deps.md` to find cross-package dependencies.

Do not crawl the file tree — use the boocontext index instead.
